Result Output Contract (Frozen v1.0)

This document defines the ONLY permissible output format for the Result Plane.
Any deviation is a contract violation.

1. JSON Structure (Strict)

{
  "frame_id": "string (UUID or Hash)",
  "timestamp": "int (Unix ms)",
  "detections": [
    {
      "class_id": "int",
      "confidence": "float (0.0 - 1.0)",
      "bbox": [x, y, w, h]  // integers, absolute pixels
    }
  ],
  "model": {
    "name": "string",
    "version": "string",
    "hash": "string"
  }
}


2. Rules

detections: Can be empty list []. Must never be null.

bbox: Must be strictly [x, y, w, h]. No [x1, y1, x2, y2].

No Versioning: The schema is fixed for v1. No v field.

No Extensibility: Extra fields in detections are ignored/dropped.

3. Authority

Producer: Detection Service (Sole Authority).

Consumer: Result Plane (Read-Only).